sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "accounts" INNER JOIN "follows" ON "accounts"."id" = "follows"."account_id" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND LOWER("accounts"."domain") = 'example.com' LIMIT $2

SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND ("statuses"."visibility" IN ($2, $3) OR EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM mentions m JOIN accounts a ON m.account_id = a.id WHERE lower(a.domain) = 'example.com')) AND "statuses"."id" = $4 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC
